tickets, [598569,93,"dPS9kyuyur3zYrab7jnrAJ",null,"b516sOlY8r3PPQeJe5afGb","filename in email",3,"the email should be able to contain not only \"a file has been made available for you\" but also what the name of the file is.\n\nThat brings the variables in the email template to:\n-name of sender\n-email address of sender\n-file name\n-file size\n-file expiration date\n-download url\n\nProposal for new standard email template:\n\nTo recipient,\n\nThe following file has been made available for you by <name>:\n\nFilename:\nFilesize:\n\nThe file will be available for you until <expiration date> on the following location:\n   <link>\n\nPlease email <name> at jan.meijer@uninett.no for information regarding\nthis file.\n\nThank you\n...\n\n\n\n\n\n\n","2009-11-04T14:13:21.000+00:00","2015-11-11T10:46:18.000+00:00",345073,null,"dPS9kyuyur3zYrab7jnrAJ","2009-12-17T06:40:52.000+00:00",0.0,0,-12.0,0,0,447388,0,0.0,0.0,0.0,0.0,"2015-11-11T10:46:18.000+00:00",null]
