tickets, [1631737,236,"bkpnJ4jEWr37jceJe5afGb","bkpnJ4jEWr37jceJe5afGb","b516sOlY8r3PPQeJe5afGb","gears upload fails when disabling third party cookies in FF",3,"Reproducible with Firefox 3.5.10 on OS X and FF 3.6.4 on Win7 after deselecting the 'Accept third party cookies' option in FF. Flash upload still works, it's only the gears upload that fails. In the back-end fs_gears_upload.php doesn't get an authorisation ($authsaml is undefined) when third party cookies are disabled in the browser.","2010-06-24T20:03:03.000+00:00","2011-09-21T23:55:15.000+00:00",345073,null,"bkpnJ4jEWr37jceJe5afGb,aNSALiyQSr3482eJe5cbCb","2010-10-27T05:41:41.000+00:00",0.0,0,236.0,0,0,447388,0,0.0,0.0,0.0,0.0,null,null]
