tickets, [2292617,309,"aNSALiyQSr3482eJe5cbCb",null,"b516sOlY8r3PPQeJe5afGb","Upload progress steps no longer listed in GUI",3,"When uploading a file using Flash, in previous releases upload progress steps were displayed on the right-hand side of the GUI (with Gears other text appeared in an editable box, see #275):\n\nUploading [...]\nFile uploaded \nMoving File \nFile Moved\n\nIn 0.1.16.1, there is no text displayed at all. However the same text with an additional step is listed when using apps3 with Flash, although only the first line appears during upload and the rest appears when clicking on the \"New Upload\" button after the upload has completed (with Gears the other text still appears but the box is no longer editable):\n\nUploading [...]\nFile uploaded \nMoving File \nFile Moved\nChecking uploaded file","2010-10-15T07:47:55.000+00:00","2011-09-21T23:36:27.000+00:00",345073,null,"aNSALiyQSr3482eJe5cbCb","2010-10-18T10:34:19.000+00:00",0.0,0,309.0,0,0,342706,0,0.0,0.0,0.0,0.0,null,null]
