tickets, [3569475,387,"dPS9kyuyur3zYrab7jnrAJ","dPS9kyuyur3zYrab7jnrAJ","b516sOlY8r3PPQeJe5afGb","Get list of FileSender \"release candidate test\" sites",3,"The software lifecycle specs state that when we release a FileSender code package as a release candidate, it has to run on at least two sites -with a useful number of users- without error for at least 1 week before said release candidate is re-branded as a release.  We need a list of sites willing to run release candidate code.\n\nBTW, we *also* need a list of beta-test sites.  Sites willing to set up and maintain beta test installs that have a useful user base.","2011-04-07T17:22:36.000+00:00","2016-02-26T13:53:32.000+00:00",213323,null,"dPS9kyuyur3zYrab7jnrAJ,aNSALiyQSr3482eJe5cbCb,b8-41KDuKr344jeJe5cbLA","2016-02-26T13:53:32.000+00:00",0.0,0,387.0,0,0,3316353,0,0.0,0.0,0.0,0.0,"2016-02-26T13:53:32.000+00:00",null]
