tickets, [4213374,435,"aNSALiyQSr3482eJe5cbCb",null,"b516sOlY8r3PPQeJe5afGb","Default maximum expiry date issues",3,"For an authenticated upload, issuing a voucher and uploading a file using a voucher: \n\n* the user must select an expiry date, while in 1.0.1 this was set automatically to the default maximum unless changed by the user\n* when selecting the expiry date, it defaults to the first available (i.e. following) day, while in 1.0.1 this defaulted to the maximum date\n\n(Note: if the user tries to manually overtype the selected expiry date to amend it to an invalid date, the expiry date *is* set to the maximum).","2011-06-21T09:27:13.000+00:00","2011-09-22T08:15:57.000+00:00",394418,null,"aNSALiyQSr3482eJe5cbCb,b8-41KDuKr344jeJe5cbLA","2011-07-01T11:21:07.000+00:00",0.0,0,435.0,0,0,447388,0,0.0,0.0,0.0,0.0,null,null]
