tickets, [4246200,450,"dPS9kyuyur3zYrab7jnrAJ",null,"b516sOlY8r3PPQeJe5afGb","Mandatory field logic",3,"When you select a file before you fill out the To: field or agree to the terms-of-use (if activated) then you are already prompted with a red flag: please fill out those fields.  You would expect the checks on mandatory fields to occur when someone tries to start an upload without all the mandatory fields being filled out.\n\nAlso: mandatory fields ought to be recognisable, like they are in 1.0.1 :)  With bold, possibly with a different colour?  Maybe green?  Not red, red is \"alert, something wrong\".  We want \"ah, that is something i must fill out and it makes sense\" :)  ","2011-06-23T13:43:29.000+00:00","2012-04-22T17:06:46.000+00:00",394418,null,"dPS9kyuyur3zYrab7jnrAJ,aNSALiyQSr3482eJe5cbCb,b8-41KDuKr344jeJe5cbLA","2011-08-15T08:35:16.000+00:00",0.0,0,450.0,0,0,447388,0,0.0,0.0,0.0,0.0,null,null]
