tickets, [4399352,467,"d4oZSslSur3R7LeJe5aVNr",null,"b516sOlY8r3PPQeJe5afGb","IE on Windows 7 issue",3,"   One of our users using windows 7 and IE (see attachments for\nversions) bombed out when  using  cloudstor.  It worked perfectly  on\nthe same box with firefox.\n\nIs there an issue with Cloudstor and Windows 7?\n\nThe IE that appeared to have problems is 8.0.7600.16385, the version of Flash is 10.3.181.26.\n\n","2011-07-11T23:24:47.000+00:00","2012-07-02T06:59:04.000+00:00",345073,null,",aNSALiyQSr3482eJe5cbCb,b8-41KDuKr344jeJe5cbLA","2012-07-02T06:59:04.000+00:00",0.0,0,467.0,0,0,342706,0,0.0,0.0,0.0,0.0,null,null]
tickets, [4409192,468,"cqcmdkRjmr4lZSeJe4gwI3","bkpnJ4jEWr37jceJe5afGb","b516sOlY8r3PPQeJe5afGb","Self-signed certificates problems vs official documentation",3,"Hi,\n\nI would like to strongly suggest to change the official installation [1] manuals to NOT include generating of a self-signed certificate since Flash only works with self-signed certificates in Internet Explorer and results in famous Flash 2038 IO Error when trying to upload a file using all non-IE browsers (both Linux and Windows). It seems to be a Flash issue [2], but it is rather hard to figure it out from very generic \"#2038 IO Error\" message code.\nI know that the instructions say: \"Be sure to get a real certificate since filesender won't work with snakeoil certificates.\" but if  these steps are not valid and must be replaced (with fairly different steps), why to include them in the first place?\n\nWe have spent a considerable amount of time to track this down so it maybe worth to include the \"2038 error\" in the related FAQ [3] for people getting the error not realizing it works with http.\n\nCheers\nJiri Horky\n\n[1] http://www.assembla.com/spaces/file_sender/wiki/Installation_-_Debian_Ubuntu\n[2] http://bugs.adobe.com/jira/browse/FP-201\n[3] http://www.assembla.com/wiki/show/file_sender/FAQ#71202d207369746520776f726b732077697468206874747020627574206e6f7420776974682068747470732c20756e636c656172206572726f72732e","2011-07-12T14:50:14.000+00:00","2011-07-20T17:02:24.000+00:00",106130,null,"cqcmdkRjmr4lZSeJe4gwI3,aNSALiyQSr3482eJe5cbCb,b8-41KDuKr344jeJe5cbLA,bkpnJ4jEWr37jceJe5afGb,dPS9kyuyur3zYrab7jnrAJ","2011-07-20T17:02:24.000+00:00",0.0,0,468.0,0,0,447388,0,0.0,0.0,0.0,0.0,null,null]
