tickets, [4624769,486,"db6iRMVOqr4jANeJe4gwI3",null,"b516sOlY8r3PPQeJe5afGb","Configuration problem with SAML",3,"Hello,\n\nI have filesender and SimpleSAMLphp installed on my system and now I can\nlog in into SimpleSAML, but all I get is the SAML status page saying\nthat I'm logged in and showing my credentials. I never go back to\nfilesender and therefore I'm never able to configure FileSender.\n\nI authenticate to a local LDAP server and that's all working fine.\n\nI guess I made a configuration error, but after Googling/reading and\ntesting for several days I don't seem to get any closer to the solution.\n\nIs there anybody that can give me a push into the right direction?\n\nThanks in advance,\n\tTonK","2011-08-04T10:53:10.000+00:00","2011-08-04T17:08:42.000+00:00",null,null,",aNSALiyQSr3482eJe5cbCb,b8-41KDuKr344jeJe5cbLA","2011-08-04T17:08:42.000+00:00",0.0,0,486.0,0,0,342706,0,0.0,0.0,0.0,0.0,null,null]
