tickets, [7557243,564,"dPS9kyuyur3zYrab7jnrAJ","bkpnJ4jEWr37jceJe5afGb","b516sOlY8r3PPQeJe5afGb","Update features, requirements, known issues, upgrade notes, end user docs & home page",3,"From Wendy's later email and subsequent discussions:\n- change \"Features\" to \"Features for v1-0\"; create new page \"Features for 1-1\"; update Features list on homepage and add a link to new page for 1.1\n- change \"Requirements\" to \"Requirements for v1-0\"; create new page \"Requirements for 1-1\"; amend the Requirements list on the homepage, adding a link to new page for 1.1 and perhaps reducing the list to a shorter summary, for example: *Client:* Web browser; Flash Player 10.x browser plugin (FileSender 1.x and 1.1); Google Gears browser plugin (FileSender 1.x only; browser limitations apply). *Server:* 64-bit Linux; Webserver; PHP 5.2.10+; PostgreSQL 8.3.9+ database; SimpleSamlPHP 1.5.1-1.6.3 (FileSender 1.0.0) or 1.7.0 (FileSender 1.0.1 and 1.1); Mail Transport Agent (MTA).\n- retain \"Known issues in v1-0\" (perhaps add a note re. subsequent fixes in 1.1); create new \"Known issues for v1-1\"\n- change \"Upgrade Notes\" to \"Upgrade Notes for v1-0\"; create new \"Upgrade Notes for v1-1\"\n- change \"End User Documentation\" to \"End User Documentation for v1.0\"; create \"End User Documentation for v1.1\" with the same text but new screenshots - mostly as an html download as suggested by Jan; update End User Documentation link on homepage (Wendy)\n- change \"Documentation for v1-0\" to \"Documentation for v1-x\" and update the page listing there","2011-10-04T12:46:43.000+00:00","2011-11-26T09:52:31.000+00:00",593383,null,"dPS9kyuyur3zYrab7jnrAJ,aNSALiyQSr3482eJe5cbCb,b8-41KDuKr344jeJe5cbLA,bkpnJ4jEWr37jceJe5afGb","2011-11-26T09:52:31.000+00:00",0.0,0,564.0,0,0,447388,0,0.0,0.0,0.0,0.0,null,null]
