tickets, [17980973,688,"aNSALiyQSr3482eJe5cbCb","aNSALiyQSr3482eJe5cbCb","b516sOlY8r3PPQeJe5afGb","Select Selenium Remote Control \"driver\" to export scripts from Selenium-IDE",3,"For the project PHP would be appropriate, however Python or Java may be considered as alternatives. Code selection is dependent on which are supported by Selenium, as well as which browsers the code drivers support. In consultation with all members of core development team. Once driver has been selected, export Selenium-IDE scripts for expansion and use with Selenium Server.","2012-03-30T03:29:18.000+00:00","2012-03-30T03:29:18.000+00:00",1051963,null,"aNSALiyQSr3482eJe5cbCb,b8-41KDuKr344jeJe5cbLA",null,0.0,0,688.0,0,1,28660,1,0.0,0.0,0.0,0.0,null,null]
