tickets, [21389323,744,"bkpnJ4jEWr37jceJe5afGb","dPS9kyuyur3zYrab7jnrAJ","b516sOlY8r3PPQeJe5afGb","Feature change request: Default HTML5URL link",3,"As per the discussion on filesender-dev: \n\nThe link to http://caniuse.com/#feat=fileapi from the help page shows the actually needed feature to be able to do HTML5 uploads. However the default link in $config['HTML5URL'] points to a more general HTML5 feature check page.\n\nQuoting Thijs:\n\n\"Perhaps this would be a better default for HTML5URL than the current\nsetting:\n        $config['HTML5URL'] = 'http://html5test.com/';\nas the caniuse one specifically targets this HTML5 feature and not any\npossible HTML5 capability.\"\n\nOn a side note: although technically HTML5 is used for large file uploads a user is probably only interested in the answer to the 'larger than 2GB possible?'\n (yes/no) question. We might consider changing the use of 'HTML5'-enabled to something stating 'Large uploads possible'.","2012-05-16T09:04:21.000+00:00","2013-03-03T15:24:32.000+00:00",394418,null,"bkpnJ4jEWr37jceJe5afGb,dPS9kyuyur3zYrab7jnrAJ","2013-03-03T15:24:32.000+00:00",0.0,0,5.0,0,1,447388,0,1.0,1.0,0.0,0.0,"2013-03-03T15:24:32.000+00:00",null]
tickets, [21443393,745,"bkpnJ4jEWr37jceJe5afGb","bkpnJ4jEWr37jceJe5afGb","b516sOlY8r3PPQeJe5afGb","Language tag comparison broken for less preferred languages",3,"When comparing browser language tags with defined languages 'weighted' tags won't work because the weight isn't stripped from the tag. This happens when the most preferred browser language is *not* defined for filesender but one of the lesse preferred browser language is. For example:\n\n    [0] => af\n    [1] => nl;q=0.9\n    [2] => en-us;q=0.8\n    [3] => en;q=0.7\n    [4] => de;q=0.6\n    [5] => it-ch;q=0.5\n    [6] => no;q=0.5\n    [7] => nb;q=0.4\n    [8] => sl;q=0.3\n    [9] => it;q=0.2\n\naf (Afrikaans) is not available but dutch (nl) is but that one won't be selected because of the exact string comparison. \n\nSpotted and patch supplied by Csillag Tamas.","2012-05-16T19:55:57.000+00:00","2012-05-17T12:35:32.000+00:00",394418,null,"bkpnJ4jEWr37jceJe5afGb","2012-05-17T12:35:32.000+00:00",0.0,0,739.0,0,1,447388,0,1.0,1.0,0.0,0.0,null,null]
