tickets, [29839653,798,"aTWq58rMCr4ysmacwqjQXA",null,"b516sOlY8r3PPQeJe5afGb","Median file size statistic",3,"Future functionality suggestion by Ingrid Melve: display the file size [[url:http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Median|median]] on the \"key statistics\" page.\n\nThis is not necessarily straight-forward to do in SQL. See notes on possible solutions for [[url:http://wiki.postgresql.org/wiki/Aggregate_Median|PostgreSQL]] and [[url:http://stackoverflow.com/questions/1291152/simple-way-to-calculate-median-with-mysql|MySQL]]. ","2012-08-14T13:15:54.000+00:00","2016-02-26T13:20:33.000+00:00",1504963,null,"aTWq58rMCr4ysmacwqjQXA","2016-02-26T13:20:33.000+00:00",0.0,0,6.0,0,1,3316353,0,1.0,1.0,0.0,0.0,"2016-02-26T13:20:33.000+00:00",null]
