tickets, [36818403,832,"aNSALiyQSr3482eJe5cbCb",null,"b516sOlY8r3PPQeJe5afGb","Link to voucher url in Guest Voucher table",3,"When several vouchers have been issued to the same recipient with the same expiry date, and then one or more of them is used or deleted, a url to the voucher in the Guest Voucher table would make it easier for the voucher issuer to confirm the url(s) of still-active voucher(s). ","2012-10-25T06:30:02.000+00:00","2012-10-26T02:47:43.000+00:00",114011,null,"aNSALiyQSr3482eJe5cbCb",null,0.0,0,30.0,0,1,28660,1,1.0,1.0,0.0,0.0,"2012-10-25T06:30:02.000+00:00",null]
