tickets, [58427433,940,"bIiF-SXuOr4ydAacwqjQWU",null,"b516sOlY8r3PPQeJe5afGb","Isolate 'Help' menu to Flash OR HTML5",4,"The user should only be given specific help details based on the page they are on. HTML5 users have no need to use Flash content so this should be removed for multiupload.php.\nFlash users would need to know how to use the flash content and steps required to upgrade to HTML5 (with the bonus' of doing so).  ","2013-07-02T09:31:50.000+00:00","2013-10-25T14:28:48.000+00:00",3839423,null,"bIiF-SXuOr4ydAacwqjQWU","2013-10-25T14:28:48.000+00:00",0.0,0,-26.0,0,0,342706,0,1.0,1.0,0.0,0.0,"2013-10-25T14:28:48.000+00:00",null]
