tickets, [67430493,1019,"d4oZSslSur3R7LeJe5aVNr","bIiF-SXuOr4ydAacwqjQWU","b516sOlY8r3PPQeJe5afGb","MySQL Error Integrity constraint violation",3,"Errors response from server when attempting to upload a file.\nE_ERROR: SQLSTATE[23000]: Integrity constraint violation: 1048 Column 'filenumdownloads' cannot be null\n\nTo Reproduce:\nRun MYSQL script to create a new database\nUpload a file using the new created database.\n","2013-10-13T00:28:28.000+00:00","2013-10-15T11:57:43.000+00:00",3839423,null,",bIiF-SXuOr4ydAacwqjQWU","2013-10-15T11:57:43.000+00:00",0.0,0,-88.0,0,0,447388,0,1.0,1.0,0.0,0.0,"2013-10-15T11:57:43.000+00:00",null]
tickets, [67688843,1020,"aTWq58rMCr4ysmacwqjQXA","aTWq58rMCr4ysmacwqjQXA","b516sOlY8r3PPQeJe5afGb","Make \"add recipient\" dialog multi-file aware",3,"The files.php dialog for adding a recipient to a transaction includes file size and file name, which are relevant only to a single file. The dialog title is \"Add new recipient\", which does not reflect that you can add multiple recipients at a time.","2013-10-15T16:08:53.000+00:00","2013-10-15T16:11:17.000+00:00",3839423,null,"aTWq58rMCr4ysmacwqjQXA","2013-10-15T16:11:17.000+00:00",0.0,0,-89.0,0,0,447388,0,1.0,1.0,0.0,0.0,"2013-10-15T16:11:17.000+00:00",null]
tickets, [67692903,1021,"aTWq58rMCr4ysmacwqjQXA","aTWq58rMCr4ysmacwqjQXA","b516sOlY8r3PPQeJe5afGb","Merge \"More settings\" and \"Advanced Settings\"",3,"These two expandable divs (on the upload page) can probably be merged into a single div, as they will both contain settings that can be enabled/disabled through config file. ","2013-10-15T16:48:12.000+00:00","2013-11-02T19:12:24.000+00:00",3839423,null,"aTWq58rMCr4ysmacwqjQXA,bIiF-SXuOr4ydAacwqjQWU",null,0.0,0,-90.0,0,0,238024,1,1.0,1.0,0.0,0.0,"2013-10-25T14:02:11.000+00:00",null]
tickets, [68137423,1022,"d4oZSslSur3R7LeJe5aVNr",null,"b516sOlY8r3PPQeJe5afGb","IE 10 Compatibility mode script error",3,"When I use an IE 10 with compatibility view activated I can't choose date and neither choose a file. Is it a known bug?\nReported by Iñigo Rodriguez.\n\nLooks like it may be an IE10 Compatibility mode browser issue.\n\nhttps://connect.microsoft.com/IE/feedback/details/774078\n\nhttp://bugs.jquery.com/ticket/12577\n\nIE 10 compativility mode causes a \"SCRIPT3: Member not found\" script error which stops all scripts.\n\nWithout being able to fix the issue in IE we can add \n<meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge\"> to the head of index.php and this will force IE to not use compativility mode. Stops the issue happening if someone tries to use IE10-Compatibility mode.\n\nDoesn’t solve the issue of what is really causing the problem which seems to be a browser issue.\n","2013-10-20T01:12:14.000+00:00","2013-10-20T01:12:36.000+00:00",394418,null,"",null,0.0,0,-32.0,0,0,28660,1,1.0,1.0,0.0,0.0,"2013-10-20T01:12:14.000+00:00",null]
tickets, [68189123,1023,"d4oZSslSur3R7LeJe5aVNr","aNSALiyQSr3482eJe5cbCb","b516sOlY8r3PPQeJe5afGb","AUP reset after logout",3,"When using 1.6-qtest, if I upload a file and logoff, then log back on during the same browser session (entering the Feide OpenIdP credentails again, so not still logged in with IdP), the AUP box remains checked. Is this expected? If I quit the browser session (clearing cookies and cache) and logon again, the AUP box is not checked, as I would expect. [For 1.5,] After logging on, uploading a file, logging off and back on during the same browser session, the AUP box is no longer checked [which] is what I expected for 1.6. Submitted by Wendy.","2013-10-21T08:26:01.000+00:00","2013-10-30T04:26:53.000+00:00",3026383,null,",aNSALiyQSr3482eJe5cbCb","2013-10-30T04:26:53.000+00:00",0.0,0,-51.0,0,0,447388,0,1.0,1.0,0.0,0.0,"2013-10-30T04:26:53.000+00:00",null]
tickets, [68718263,1024,"aTWq58rMCr4ysmacwqjQXA","aTWq58rMCr4ysmacwqjQXA","b516sOlY8r3PPQeJe5afGb","Script to send a stats summary by email to site admin",3,"Create a script that sends a summary of key statistics (e.g. numbers of users, upload, downloads, active files and a comparison to previous month) by email to the site admin. Should be institution specific in cases where such information is included with user credentials (will need an additional logs table field).  \n\nCould be done as an optional cron job. Storing parsed data in an additional DB table specifically for this purpose might be best, although all stats can be retrieved from the logs table.\n\nInput Xander: if org-attribuut then instelling = org-attribuut else instelling = domein authuseremail\n\nImplement stats both as email and once queries are settled, implement as \"stats\" tab.\n\nAbout access control: lets start with what we concluded in the stats module but without the \"user\".  \n$config['stats_access_level'] = 'statsadmin'; // Who can access stats page. Possible settings are 'statsadmin', 'public' or 'disabled'. A more restrictive setting here would override the access settings below.\n\nTo start with the key stats from the stats module are probably useful.  Would be wonderful to have those key stats both per filesender instans and per institution.   Would also be helpful to be able to indicate different timeperiods (up to 10?) you'd like to see next to eachother for easy comparison, for example key stats for 2010-2013, or for march 2012 vs. march 2013, especially when thinking of visiting institutions for marketing purposes etc.\n\n*Note: we do need to discuss the need for anonimisation/aggregation: do we already do this for a simple stats function in 2.0 \"asap\" or would we postpone it to after we have the key numbers?*  First thought: let us focus on making key numbers per instans and site available ASAP, based on current database tables.  Phase 2: once key stats have stabilised, work out proper way for anonimisation and aggregation, possibly prepared for phase 3: allow sending aggregates/anonimised stats to centralised collector.  Phase 4: pretty pictures.\n","2013-10-25T14:54:28.000+00:00","2014-03-20T09:10:21.000+00:00",3839423,null,"aTWq58rMCr4ysmacwqjQXA",null,0.0,0,-92.0,0,0,3316333,1,3.0,3.0,0.0,0.0,"2014-03-20T09:10:21.000+00:00",null]
tickets, [68719483,1025,"aTWq58rMCr4ysmacwqjQXA","dPS9kyuyur3zYrab7jnrAJ","b516sOlY8r3PPQeJe5afGb","Security code for downloads",3,"Allow uploader to optionally specify a security code for transactions, which will need to be entered by the downloader in order to download the files. Three invalid attempts should \"lock\" the download until it is reopened by uploader. \n\nMight need anti-spambot measures?","2013-10-25T15:05:30.000+00:00","2014-03-26T08:35:12.000+00:00",3839423,null,"aTWq58rMCr4ysmacwqjQXA,dPS9kyuyur3zYrab7jnrAJ",null,0.0,0,-93.0,0,0,3325193,1,3.0,3.0,0.0,0.0,"2014-03-26T08:35:12.000+00:00",null]
tickets, [68719773,1026,"aTWq58rMCr4ysmacwqjQXA","dPS9kyuyur3zYrab7jnrAJ","b516sOlY8r3PPQeJe5afGb","Changes to admin.php",4,"In connection with a technical overhaul of the admin panel (new table layout, bug fixes), it would be convenient to discuss and rethink any changes to the information that the admin panel contains in 2.0. E.g. representation of multi-file transactions, email settings or more sophisticated statistics.\n\nDiscussion appreciated.","2013-10-25T15:08:12.000+00:00","2014-03-16T21:12:40.000+00:00",3839423,null,"aTWq58rMCr4ysmacwqjQXA,dPS9kyuyur3zYrab7jnrAJ",null,0.0,0,-94.0,0,0,28660,1,3.0,3.0,0.0,0.0,"2013-10-25T15:08:12.000+00:00",null]
