tickets, [86457763,1090,"aNSALiyQSr3482eJe5cbCb",null,"b516sOlY8r3PPQeJe5afGb","UI display issues",3,"The following UI display issues have been observed (as first highlighted in #819):\n1. When first clicking on the expiry date field during a browser session, the arrows in the expiry date popup take a moment to appear\n2. When first pointing to one of the arrows in the expiry date popup (once they have appeared), it vanishes momentarily then reappears\n3. The close symbol (X) in the upload progress popup also takes a moment longer to load than the rest of the popup\n4. The drag lines in the bottom right-hand corner of the \"Help\" and \"About\" dialogue boxes, to indicate that the box can be resized, are missing\n5. When clicking on the \"Help\" or \"About\" buttons then \"Close\" button the cursor is stuck on the first (\"Help\" or \"About\") button (blinking cursor inside button, box visible around button, target url displayed).\n","2014-05-15T06:40:33.000+00:00","2014-06-30T14:04:48.000+00:00",3026383,null,"aNSALiyQSr3482eJe5cbCb",null,0.0,0,-80.0,0,0,3325193,1,1.0,1.0,0.0,0.0,"2014-06-30T14:04:48.000+00:00",null]
