tickets, [152552443,1318,"c9JOC0LeOr5BTmacwqEsg8","dgRDGuZ4ar478MacwqEsg8","b516sOlY8r3PPQeJe5afGb","auth_remote_signature_algorithm is not used",3,"The configuration manual mentions `auth_remote_signature_algorithm` but no matter how I set it, the Files.sha1 field is never populated.","2016-07-01T06:25:32.000+00:00","2016-07-01T06:25:33.000+00:00",6605143,null,"c9JOC0LeOr5BTmacwqEsg8,dgRDGuZ4ar478MacwqEsg8",null,0.0,0,-130.0,0,1,28660,1,0.0,0.0,0.0,0.0,"2016-07-01T06:25:32.000+00:00",null]
tickets, [155078393,1319,"c9JOC0LeOr5BTmacwqEsg8","dgRDGuZ4ar478MacwqEsg8","b516sOlY8r3PPQeJe5afGb","Configuration parsing in REST can lead to flags inadvertedly set to false.",2,"Referring to r3953, the new code path neglects to read the default values for configuration flags when the user has not provided any configuration flags itself. The system simply returns an empty array in this case, which defaults all flags to \"false\". This may cause strange surprises when using the REST API and expecting that flags in the configuration file are enforced.","2016-07-22T11:38:35.000+00:00","2016-09-13T11:26:06.000+00:00",6605143,null,"c9JOC0LeOr5BTmacwqEsg8,dgRDGuZ4ar478MacwqEsg8","2016-09-13T11:26:06.000+00:00",0.0,0,-131.0,0,1,447388,0,1.0,1.0,0.0,0.0,"2016-09-13T11:26:06.000+00:00",null]
tickets, [157328863,1320,"c9JOC0LeOr5BTmacwqEsg8","dPS9kyuyur3zYrab7jnrAJ","b516sOlY8r3PPQeJe5afGb","Log a warning when observed protocol is more secure than site_url",3,"Strange things can happen when FileSender is served via HTTPS but the <code>site_url</code> mentions http. In this case, the user was able to log in but not upload, the error message was <code>terasender_source_file_not_available</code> which of course is not very descriptive.\n\nI suggest the following behaviour:\n\nIf <code>$_SERVER['HTTPS'] && $_SERVER['HTTPS'] != 'off'</code> and <code>site_url</code> does *not* start with <code>https://</code>, then log a warning.\n\nThe reason for not detecting the opposite, is that the detection may be fooled by a reverse proxy.","2016-08-17T11:45:42.000+00:00","2016-08-17T11:45:42.000+00:00",6605143,null,"c9JOC0LeOr5BTmacwqEsg8,dPS9kyuyur3zYrab7jnrAJ",null,0.0,0,-132.0,0,1,28660,1,1.0,1.0,0.0,0.0,"2016-08-17T11:45:42.000+00:00",null]
